_sText:
This is one of my first maps i did for cs 1.6. 

But i decided to port it to CS Source. just for fun and also because i wanted to play it with player ragdolls and better looking water. 

The map is small, it has 2 bomb sites, one in an aztec themed place and the other in a dust themed place. 

Its a 4 vs 4 map.
